  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      we designed this randomized, single -blind, prospective clinical study to test postoperative&#xD;
      analgesia of three intrathecal additives in elective caesarean sections which are magnesium,&#xD;
      dexamethasone and dexmedetomidine.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
